          <para>Position the pump on the pad and install the four mounting bolts.
          Torque the bolts to 25 Nm in a cross pattern.</para>
        </proceduralStep>
        <proceduralStep>
          <para>Connect the supply and pressure lines. Torque the fittings to 18 Nm.</para>
        </proceduralStep>
        <proceduralStep>
          <para>Do a hydraulic system leak check at idle power.</para>
        </proceduralStep>
      </mainProcedure>
